  <name>CCDciel</name>
  <summary>CCD capture software for the amateur astronomer</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      A CCD capture software intended for the amateur astronomer.
    </p>
    <p>
      It includes all the features required to perform digital imaging CCD observation
      of celestial objects.
    </p>
    <p>
      Using the standard drivers protocol INDI and ASCOM it can connect and control the CCD camera,
      the focuser, the filter wheel and the telescope mount.
    </p>
  </description>

